</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_linking_a_property_to_an_item">1.2. Linking a property to an item</h3>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Item » Edit item » Open item » Tab: Properties</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Activate the property you have just set up in the section <strong>Activate further properties</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Save the settings for the item</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the desired value in the desired language in the section <strong>Properties</strong>. The language should be the same as the language which was selected in the format settings for the corresponding Elastic Export.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_assigning_the_property">1.3. Assigning the property</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In order to allocate the column <strong>free_text_field</strong>, please contact your contact person at idealo. Your contact person will set up the allocation of the column <strong>free_text_field</strong> for you.</p>
</div>
